1.1.4 PROJECT ASSUMPTION: 
Stakeholder Assumptions: 
• When filling property details and bond records, tenants will be honest in their 
information. 
• The project supervisor will also offer feedback in time when it comes to requirement 
validation and testing. 
• Skillup Labs will be the project sponsor and offer the needed support. 
User-Related Assumptions: 
• End users (tenants) are fairly computer literate and able to navigate a web application. 
• The users will be guided on document uploads and data entry. 
• Users have access to a computer or mobile device that is connected to the internet. 
Technical Assumptions: 
• Users have a modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge). 
5 
• The environment used will have adequate storage and processing capacity. 
• The development environment (Node.js, PostgreSQL) is not going to change during 
the project. 
Operational Assumptions: 
• The team members will accomplish their tasks within the 12-week schedule. 
• To monitor progress, team meetings will take place weekly. 
• Before the deployment of the system, it will be thoroughly tested.
